{"tid":2225481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"明文規管高層異己 缺乏信心","createTime":"2020-10-01T11:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T11:01:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"67096222232ae45e80531abb2f0d828ecf6dfc8b","tid":2225481,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:00:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201001/I5AQYL7WJFCT5M3GDP3FM5WWAQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201001%2FI5AQYL7WJFCT5M3GDP3FM5WWAQ%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=3988afe7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201001%2FI5AQYL7WJFCT5M3GDP3FM5WWAQ%2F&h=af0b0d3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201001/I5AQYL7WJFCT5M3GDP3FM5WWAQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n明文規管高層異己 缺乏信心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/g2x1Jsh3rktFfQEy5DShzj7RZGE=/1395x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FPIW4KOLZRCFDCMOULGNGL7UNI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fg2x1Jsh3rktFfQEy5DShzj7RZGE%3D%2F1395x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFPIW4KOLZRCFDCMOULGNGL7UNI.jpg&h=2b8436a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中共造神無所不至，在柬埔寨推出《習近平談治國理政》。新華社<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中共在今年訂立最少三個「工作條例」，由企業至黨基層幹部都有，均有類似「政治上行動上以習近平同志爲核心的黨中央保持高度一致」，但工作條例上升至中央委員會則是首次。<br />\n<br />\n中央委員會是中共核心權力機構，有204委員及100多名候補委員。中央委員權力在於能選舉政治局成員、政治局常委及中共總書記。。。。。。。。。。。。因此他相信習想用這些工作條例綁住不支持自己的高層，從而鏟除。<br />\n<br />\n劉銳紹又指，此事從側面可看出習近平欠缺信心。他說：「鄧小平連軍委都交給江澤民，自己仍能控制江澤民，鄧本身就是權威，很有信心。相反現在習近平任何事都要寫下，然後才『依法』辦事，其實是最無信心表現。」"},{"pid":"513bd1cc0078d0a2858e8d801c00072c7df96f9f","tid":2225481,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:01:06.000Z","msg":"21世紀希特拉"}]}